 <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">We discuss a method to reconstruct two-dimensional proton bunch densities using vertex distributions from LHC beam-beam scans. The x-y correlations in the beam shapes are studied and a luminosity calibration technique is introduced. The method is demonstrated using simulated beam-beam scans. We evaluate the impact of non-factorization features for beam shapes of double-Gaussian type.</subfield>
  <subfield code="9">IOP</subfield>
 </datafield>
